  "title": "TEMP ADMIN ASSISTANTS NEEDED!! ($10.50/H) #HCGT",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p><p>-         Support on boarding process and preparing of documents</p><p>-         Scheduling interviews and meetings</p><p>-         Providing general administrative support to HR team</p><p>-         Maintaining employee records and updating HR databases</p><p>-         Work effectively in our team-based & collaborative environment to deliver top quality supply of talents and candidates</p><p>-         Other ad-hoc duties</p><p>Job Requirements:</p><p>-         Minimum A Level/Diploma</p><p>-         Office Hours 5 days</p><p>-         Proficient in Microsoft Office</p><p>-         Strong organizational and time management skills</p><p>-         Experience in Admin/HR will be highly preferred</p><p>All qualified applicants, please send in your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>Tricia Celestine Goh (R1981653)<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No.199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>",
